WEBVTT

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:02.840
In Lebanon, one
in four people is a refugee,

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:06.816
a quarter of the whole population.

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:08.936
And refugees stay for a long time.

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:11.056
The average length of displacement

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:12.280
is 10 years.

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:17.680
I went to what was the world's
largest refugee camp, in eastern Kenya.

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:19.296
It's called Dadaab.

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:21.456
It was built in 1991-92

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:25.400
as a "temporary camp"
for Somalis fleeing the civil war.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:27.120
I met Silo.

